            </owl:Restriction>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:comment>Designation of DB track assets.
zB. Weiche 5 in P-Hausen 
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;index (Kennzahl) = 60&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;localName = 5&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;shortNameLayoutPlan = W5&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;longNameLayoutPlan = 60W5&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;nameInTable = 60W5 &lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;nameOnSite = 60W5&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</rdfs:comment>
