It isolates (en-UK: &lt;i&gt;shuts in&lt;/i&gt;) the shunting yard from the main running line.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>ShutInSidingKeyReleaseInstrument</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


