        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Train_protection#TpMarker"/>
        <rdfs:comment>An ETCS marker is a spot on the track where a linear event occurs or a property changes that is relevant to ETCS signalling:
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change in National Values&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change of gradient&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change of speed&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change of track condition&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Start of text display&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

An ETCS profile is an ordered sequence of markers.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>EtcsMarker</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    


