        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#RbcProperties"/>
        <owl:disjointWith rdf:resource="https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#RbcWatchdog"/>
        <rdfs:comment>A set of telegrams that is sent under the given set of conditions applies.
Used for switchable balises.

The SRS versions allows selecting telegrams of a given version.</rdfs:comment>
